To find the average value of elements in the given array

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int [] arr = {12,13,15,6,7,8};
        int sum = 0;
        for(int i =0; i < arr.length; i++){
            sum += arr[i];
        }

        double average = sum / arr.length;
        System.out.println(average);
    }
}

Output: 10.0

